<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.10.3">
<l>eṅka ḷukkaruḷ ceykiṉṟa vīcaṉai vāca vārkuḻa lāḷmalai maṅkaitaṉ</l>
<l>paṅka ṉaipaṅkil vaittukan tāṉṟaṉṉaip pāṉmai yaippaṉi māmati yamtavaḻ</l>
<l>maṅku laiccuṭa raivaṭa māmalai yucci yainacci  nāmvaṇaṅ kappaṭum</l>
<l>kaṅku laipaka laicceṉṟu nāṭik kaṇṇa maṅkaiyuḷ kaṇṭukoṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone searching, I saw for myself in Kaṇṇamaṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">the lord who grants grace to us,</l>
<l>The one who is glad keeping on [one] half the one who is in half</l>
<l>The maid of the mountain, the one with fragrant garlands in [her] curls,</l>
<l rend="indent">[good] character, the sky where creeps the great cool moon, the sun,</l>
<l>The peak of the northern mountain, the night in which we are humbled</l>
<l rend="indent">with longing, and the day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
